Hello everyone!  


This a subreddit to get away from the middle-schoolers bragging about beating Scott for $0.23 yesterday when they had the rectangular pizza for lunch in the school cafeteria.  


This is also non-tolerant of habitual losers who can't possibly fathom that anyone actually makes money and decide to shit on everything.  


REAL PLAYERS: You can now post adult stuff without children misspelling stupid post titles, thoughts, or comments. 

I moderate a lot of polarizing subs (/r/StandUpShots) and welcome regular users who would like to me on the moderation team.  


Thank you for your patronage.
